---
// MethodComparison.astro — 3-column comparison of Fine-Tuning vs RAG vs Prompting
---

<div class="mc-wrap">
  <h3 class="mc-title">Side by Side: The Three Approaches</h3>
  <p class="mc-sub">Same goal — better LLM output. Very different trade-offs.</p>

  <div class="mc-table-wrap">
    <table class="mc-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th class="mc-th mc-th--label"></th>
          <th class="mc-th mc-th--prompt">
            <span class="mc-th-icon">✏️</span>
            <span>Prompt Engineering</span>
          </th>
          <th class="mc-th mc-th--rag">
            <span class="mc-th-icon">🔍</span>
            <span>RAG</span>
          </th>
          <th class="mc-th mc-th--ft">
            <span class="mc-th-icon">🎯</span>
            <span>Fine-Tuning</span>
          </th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td class="mc-label">Setup Time</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--good">Minutes</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--mid">Days</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--bad">Weeks</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="mc-label">Cost</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--good">$0</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--mid">$50-500/mo</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--bad">$500-5,000+</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="mc-label">New Knowledge</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--bad">No</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--good">Yes, dynamic</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--mid">Yes, static</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="mc-label">Data Needed</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--good">0 examples</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--mid">Documents</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--bad">1,000+ pairs</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="mc-label">Latency</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--good">Baseline</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--mid">+500ms-2s</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--good">Baseline</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="mc-label">Hallucination Control</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--mid">Medium</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--good">High</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--mid">Medium</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="mc-label">Updates</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--good">Edit prompt</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--good">Re-index docs</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--bad">Re-train model</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="mc-label">Best For</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--highlight mc-cell--prompt-hl">Format, tone, simple tasks</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--highlight mc-cell--rag-hl">Knowledge Q&A, search</td>
          <td class="mc-cell mc-cell--highlight mc-cell--ft-hl">Domain-specific behavior</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .mc-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
    border-radius: 16px; padding: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; border: 1px solid #334155;
  }
  .mc-title { color: #f1f5f9; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 0.25rem; }
  .mc-sub { color: #64748b; font-size: 0.8rem; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; font-family: monospace; }

  .mc-table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; }
  .mc-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.72rem; }

  .mc-th {
    padding: 10px 12px; text-align: center; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #334155;
  }
  .mc-th--label { width: 130px; }
  .mc-th--prompt { color: #4ade80; }
  .mc-th--rag { color: #06b6d4; }
  .mc-th--ft { color: #f59e0b; }
  .mc-th-icon { display: block; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 4px; }

  .mc-label {
    padding: 8px 12px; color: #94a3b8; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.7rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1e293b; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .mc-cell {
    padding: 8px 12px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #1e293b;
    font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.65rem;
  }
  .mc-cell--good { color: #4ade80; }
  .mc-cell--mid { color: #fbbf24; }
  .mc-cell--bad { color: #f87171; }

  .mc-cell--highlight { font-family: inherit; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.65rem; border-bottom: none; }
  .mc-cell--prompt-hl { color: #86efac; background: rgba(74,222,128,0.05); }
  .mc-cell--rag-hl { color: #67e8f9; background: rgba(6,182,212,0.05); }
  .mc-cell--ft-hl { color: #fde68a; background: rgba(245,158,11,0.05); }

  tbody tr { transition: background 0.2s; }
  tbody tr:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
</style>
